# P&ID Drawing: Argon Purging System - APS-3
# Facility: Bharat Steel Works Ltd.
# Drawing ID: P&ID-APS-3-001
# Revision: 2.0
# Date: 15 Jun 2025

# EQUIPMENT TAGS
APS-3: Argon Purging System
V-101: Argon Supply Valve
V-102: Purge Control Valve
P-101: Pressure Sensor
T-101: Temperature Sensor
LF-3: Ladle Furnace

# PIPING CONNECTIONS
APS-3 -> V-101 -> LF-3
APS-3 -> V-102 -> P-101
APS-3 -> T-101

# PROCESS FLOW
Argon Supply -> APS-3 -> V-101 -> LF-3 (Ladle Purging)
Argon Supply -> APS-3 -> V-102 -> P-101 (Pressure Monitoring)
APS-3 -> T-101 (Temperature Monitoring)

# SAFETY INTERLOCKS
V-101: Normally Closed - Opens on purge command
V-102: Pressure Relief - Opens at >2.5 bar
P-101: High Pressure Alarm - Triggers at 3.0 bar
T-101: High Temperature Alarm - Triggers at 500°C

# MAINTENANCE NOTES
Last Inspection: 10 Jun 2025
Next Scheduled: 10 Dec 2025
Status: Operational
Deferred Work: V-102 calibration (deferred from 01 May 2025)

# COMPLIANCE TAGS
PESO-8.3: Pressure vessel inspection required
ISO 45001-8.1.2: Near-miss escalation protocol
